PLAYER STATS HELP
STRENGTH
Strength (STR): A character's strength is a measurement of their ability to exhert force. Characters with higher strength are able to wield larger weapons and are able to hit harder with them. Strength also affects your carrying capacity and your ability to move heavy objects such as boulders and furniture.

See also: ~CREFstats, dexterity, constitution, speed, willpower, intelligence, empathy, charisma
